{"tid":1869063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支衛 : 武漢肺炎患者 82%輕微 不足2%死亡 批評各國不肯分享臨床數據","createTime":"2020-02-08T03:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T07:41:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":207,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"9153e26c9ec0d4f00b0dac14b5f70e063d1735ba","tid":1869063,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"世衛指確診新型肺炎患者約八成二病情輕微<br />\n<br />\n世衛說，在目前確診新型肺炎病例當中，大約八成二患者病情輕微，一成半嚴重，百分之三危殆，只有不足百分之二患者死亡，而且死者往往是年紀較大，本身亦有其他病患。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事譚德塞批評，部分國家至今仍未分享確診病例的臨床數據，敦促這些國家盡快分享信息，強調無沒有任何一個國家或組織，能夠單獨阻止這場疫情，形容敵人很危險，會帶來嚴重的社會、政治與經濟動盪，必須齊心協力作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507370-20200208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507370-20200208.htm&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3eaedd4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507370-20200208.htm&h=68e14767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507370-20200208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6c97654db35f7c0164285613867a03cec5ff9c31","tid":1869063,"uid":57677,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"官方數字己經:一千出院,五百死亡"},{"pid":"5ece5855128f10d1928955281d245296efb2c3ef","tid":1869063,"uid":55955,"like":155,"dislike":0,"score":155,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"中國外交部發言人譚德塞"},{"pid":"cb4b710023f975433c185711afb2f60a1652ae85","tid":1869063,"uid":68463,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"又唔危險又危險 點呀"},{"pid":"0a0bcfa8cc8a4f9be3961de3ca21898a1f84ea27","tid":1869063,"uid":121136,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"睇黎係想參考下部份國家嘅數據方便作數"},{"pid":"12fc75869ecc1eeb2bb60d0f05a04f46d95b95d3","tid":1869063,"uid":123175,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"reply