":"咪係 當初爆發果陣好似係支那唔肯同全球國家分享數據<br />\n死要面，收收埋埋，依家鬧返其他國家唔救你？？？？<br />\n支那人厚臉皮到 企隔離都覺得醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e08c9f10887a425cafe048b903d6bdb31a77bf","tid":1869063,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e799b99b694679c33f9023d4df99aa2161d9a16","tid":1869063,"uid":48330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人覺得中國個治愈人數分分鐘都係假嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"應該唔係，但確趁同死亡數字就99%假"},{"pid":"90e45fc24aa63c9441748846b817420701d962f1","tid":1869063,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6c97654db35f7c0164285613867a03cec5ff9c31","tid":1869063,"uid":57677,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"官方數字己經:一千出院,五百死亡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"數學係體育老師教？"},{"pid":"e789a5821df62500708de5c741b4aa8379992e97","tid":1869063,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"美國個患者個醫治記錄公開左全世界睇到<br />\n你支那呢？ 點醫又唔講， 一係死左一係扮出院<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母世衛"},{"pid":"59f16c71763d72097c78149109953a65d3350d3d","tid":1869063,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623252f475447aa7f13bfa7b9628cb4017eb996e","tid":1869063,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"美帝藥都俾埋仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e86e5350f7a9f27309c8e84393a570022a69d4d","tid":1869063,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-