ally, teams from the agency&rsquo;s Epidemic Intelligence Service can be in the air within 24 hours.<br />\n<br />\nBut no invitation has come &mdash; and no one can publicly explain why.<br />\n<br />\nThe World Health Organization, which made a similar offer about two weeks ago, appears to be facing the same cold shoulder, though a spokeswoman said it is just &ldquo;sorting out arrangements.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ac8d53e3669311fc9b6cb2ebd1902db8c2f7e725","tid":1869063,"uid":165136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"中國嗰度好輕微咪佢自己搞掂<br />\n人地其他國家覺得好嚴重，顧掂自己先有時間理人㗎嘛<br />\n叫人做嘢咁口響，你去做囉"},{"pid":"69f2545d48d0fa3241cfbfb3b8c570bf8a125e19","tid":1869063,"uid":130105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"公平些講，日本隻郵輪咪做緊實驗囉，封閉環境，點發病，都睇到曬，跟本唔會死人，不過前題係要醫療好；大陸真係唔係囉"},{"pid":"352f634fe7a13005ba05b62bb25e3ba76c9361e1","tid":1869063,"uid":60200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9153e26c9ec0d4f00b0dac14b5f70e063d1735ba","tid":1869063,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"世衛指確診新型肺炎患者約八成二病情輕微<br />\n<br />\n世衛說，在目前確診新型肺炎病例當中，大約八成二患者病情輕微，一成半嚴重，百分之三危殆，只有不足百分之二患者死亡，而且死者往往是年紀較大，本身亦有其他病患。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事譚德塞批評，部分國家至今仍未分享確診病例的臨床數據，敦促這些國家盡快分享信息，強調無沒有任何一個國家或組織，能夠單獨阻止這場疫情，形容敵人很危險，會帶來嚴重的社會、政治與經濟動盪，必須齊心協力作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507370-20200208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507370-20200208.htm&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3eaedd4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507370-20200208.htm&h=68e14767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507370-20200208.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"82%+15%+3%+2%=102%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\